h1. Managing users

h2. Users list

Accounts status:

* This icon !/images/locked.png! means that the account is locked. A user having a locked account cannot log in and access the application.
* This icon !/images/user_new.png! means that the user hasn't actived his account yet.

The Lock/Unlock buttons let you lock/unlock the user accounts.

h2. Adding or editing a User

A user designated as administrator has unrestricted access to the application and to all projects.

In editing mode, leave the Password field blank in order to keep the user's password unchanged.
